high_descs: Turn around and step forward to face the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Take a step to the left to face the bread on the counter.
Cut the bread on the counter into slices.
Turn around and walk forward and turn right to face the sink.
Place the knife on the edge of the sink.
Turn right and cross the room to face the bread on the counter.
Pick up a slice of bread on the counter.
Turn around and walk forward and turn right to face the microwave.
Heat the slice of bread in the microwave and remove it.
Step back to face the sink.
Place the bread on the edge of the sink.
anns.task_desc: To heat a slice of bread as well as place it on the edge of the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the stove.
Pick up the knife on the counter to the right of the stove.
Turn left and go to the counter on the left of the stove.
Cut the bread on the counter.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Put the knife on the counter in front of the left sink.
Turn right and head back to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Turn around and head to the microwave above the sink.
Warm up the slice of bread in the microwave and pick it back up.
Turn left and go to the left sink.
Put the slice of bread on the counter in front of the left sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed slice of bread on the counter in front of the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk up to the stove
Pick up the knife from the counter just right of the stove
Turn and walk left then turn right to face the counter left of the stove
Cut the bread loaf on the counter with the knife
Turn around and walk forward then turn right and walk to the sink
Put the knife down on the counter just in front of the left sink
Turn right and walk back to the counter left of the stove
Pick up a piece of bread from the counter
Turn around and walk over to the microwave above the sink
Heat the bread piece in the microwave then remove it
Walk slightly away from the counter then turn back to face it
Put the bread piece down on the counter just in front of the left sink
anns.task_desc: Put the heated bread piece on the kitchen counter
